						               													<description>Wildstorms is a CCG based on Image Comics characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A battlesite card is fought over by the characters.  Winning the battlesite wins the game.  The cards include...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Characters - these are drawn from the comics, Wild C.A.T.S., StormWatch, Team 7, Gen13 and WetWorks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Combat - these are used to affect fights.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Equipment - these are attached to characters to add to their power.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Plot Twist - these represent strokes of good or bad luck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battlesite cards - win one of these and you win the basic game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Prize - if you win a battlesite card in the campaign game you will receive one of these to use in future battles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Wildstorn Legends was an expansion that added solitaire rules.  Cards are laid out in a grid much like in Ani-Mayhem that you have to battle through to win prizes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is fascinating and the artwork is very good.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Online Play&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     CCG Workshop (no longer available)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
